item.title: How can i change the ::rules
item.dc:creator: @dragonman2 dragonman2
item.description:
@dragonman2 wrote:

[quote=“Si Force, post:2, topic:326150”]Search for “rules” in your Client.java, once you are there depending on your source it may or may not tell you that the main text is in another method, like “rules();”, for example. If it shows that just search “void rules()”.

An easier way would to just search whatever text is in rules in the same file.[/quote]thanks it worked!
